text: Avdulovo-1 () is a rural locality (a selo) in Leontyevskoye Rural Settlement of Stupinsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == The village is located on the left bank of the Sukusha River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdulovo-1
